name: Sleepwalker "Untitled" 12" - Second Press
description:
VU008 Sleepwalker "Untitled" 12"

Originally recorded between 2007 and 2009 and only available as a limited CDR,  Sleepwalker's first musical output is finally getting repressed on vinyl. This three song 12" is pressed on black vinyl and cut at 45 rpm for the highest sound quality. This record comes housed in a full color, single pocket jacket, with a 12" printed inner sleeve and a black letter pressed obi strip. Pressed in an edition of one hundred copies, Sleepwalker features Michael Rekevics of both Fell Voices and Ruin Lust.
